    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Tomli Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Tomli</application> package is a theme for
        the <application>sphinx</application> documentation system. Although
        developed separately, it is the default theme for sphinx.
      </para>

      &lfs112_checked;

